If you don&#039;t have a full time job, three months would be plenty of time. Otherwise, squeezing it in along with work, family, exercise, etc. yep it takes longer. But I think the point is don&#039;t put it off, stay in that &quot;world&quot; you are creating as much as possible.]]></description>
