<p>If you don&#8217;t have a full time job, three months would be plenty of time. Otherwise, squeezing it in along with work, family, exercise, etc. yep it takes longer. But I think the point is don&#8217;t put it off, stay in that &#8220;world&#8221; you are creating as much as possible.</p>
